{"tid":2380474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮指美國將以戰略性忍耐政策放生處理對華關係","createTime":"2021-01-26T02:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T03:10:27.000Z","uid":313054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca73f559cbb4b724d39fa6b658cc08d5ed8e1feb","tid":2380474,"uid":313054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:11:19.000Z","msg":"ow新聞台】美國白宮發言人普薩基表示，科技是美中兩國未來的競爭中心點，拜登新政府會以戰略忍耐政策處理美中關係。 <br />\n       普薩基：「我們看到過去數年，中國對內變得越來越專制，對外變得更加強勢，北京現時正明顯地挑戰我們的安全、繁榮和價值觀，美國需要以新的方法應對，我們希望以戰略忍耐策略處理，希望進行內部的跨部門評估。」<br />\n普薩基表示，未來將會與國會民主、共和兩黨議員以及國際盟友夥伴接觸，商討未來對華政策方向。<br />\n<br />\n      普薩基又指，科技是美中未來競爭的中心點，中國不惜一切，包括盜取知識產權和進行間諜活動，以取得科技優勢，拜登新政府將做好防禦工作，確保中國要為以不公平及非法手段取得美國科技負責，建立中國軍事力量，美國將需要以一個全方位的戰略應對。"},{"pid":"1157152ab0a2a19b841dcee4300e5da0ed0f9709","tid":2380474,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識撚: 對華政策已成形  冇可能一夜之間大改既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實又唔錯得哂  都等左成4晚咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f502d3ef79b205749cd74ceb29fd0eab4802e1","tid":2380474,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"點解段說話前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n又戰略忍耐 又要搵歐洲令中国負責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38ceab3fa585bcbf2b4ce5b2fc1a6dc3600e4b8","tid":2380474,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96f502d3ef79b205749cd74ceb29fd0eab4802e1","tid":2380474,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"點解段說話前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n又戰略忍耐 又要搵歐洲令中国負責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d504956fe98c451b9adb143c3220c54c50cfd3","tid":2380474,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:49:32.000Z","msg":"即係走住屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e866299eaac2df4467c0c0f476dfa4a8afbd26e8","tid":2380474,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"即係今日割五城，明日割十城 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}